T11 210 Anonymous13 : However, as the game progresses, the player will inevitably get better at facing the challenges player improvement - some faster than others of course - but a good game designer will not ignore this, and in most well-designed games the rate of increase of challenge difficulty is faster than the rate of character enhancement.
